Package: orchideecore
Title: Experimental Portable Core for ORCHIDEE RATB Indicators
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("ORCHIDEE", "Maintainers", email = "orchidee@example.invalid", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements deliberately narrow, auditable ORCHIDEE core profiles
    from a validated canonical bundle to annual Escherichia coli C3G,
    Staphylococcus aureus methicillin, and Klebsiella pneumoniae BLSE
    resistance and incidence outputs. The experiment excludes completion,
    reporting, caching, and hospital-specific extraction.
